Miami Airport Fire Disrupts Tourism, American Air, Herald Says

-- B y   P e t e r   J .   B r e n n a n
-- 
2011-03-25T16:13:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-25/miami-airport-fire-disrupts-tourism-american-air-herald-says.html
A fire that sparked cancellation of
179 flights at Miami International Airport and is disrupting the
height of tourism season may have been caused by an electrical
failure in underground pipes that delivers fuel to hundreds of
planes each day, the Miami Herald said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter J. Brennan at 
 pbrennan3@bloomberg.net  